				I finally made my way into Lavastorm recently. Most everything there conned green to me, and the only reason i was there is because I heard it was easy loot.<BR>
Ran into my first fire imp, conned green. My 19th lvl warrior scoffed, and pounced.<BR>
MAJOR NOTE: The imps have a fire engulf that is proximity based. If you are skirting the critter, this thing is a snap. If you MUST fight it melee, better hold on tight cause the sucker packs a SERIOUS punch for a greenie.<BR>
If you are a melee fighter, do NOT attempt these with fire resistance, they aren't worth the trouble...
